程序包分层结构:
  • action,
  • dao,
  • dao.impl,
  • model,
  • service,
  • service.impl,
  • util

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opensymphony.xwork2.ActionSupport (implements com.opensymphony.xwork2.Action, com.opensymphony.xwork2.LocaleProvider, java.io.Serializable, com.opensymphony.xwork2.TextProvider, com.opensymphony.xwork2.Validateable, com.opensymphony.xwork2.ValidationAware)
      • action.DownloadAction
    • dao.impl.BaseDaoImpl<T> (implements dao.BaseDao<T>)
      • dao.impl.DocDaoImpl (implements dao.DocDao)
      • dao.impl.InboxDaoImpl (implements dao.InboxDao)
      • dao.impl.UserDaoImpl (implements dao.UserDao)
    • util.Config
    • util.DateTransform
    • model.Doc (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • action.DocAction (implements com.opensymphony.xwork2.ModelDriven<T>)
    • service.impl.DocServiceImpl (implements service.DocService)
    • model.Inbox (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • action.InboxAction (implements com.opensymphony.xwork2.ModelDriven<T>)
    • service.impl.InboxServiceImpl (implements service.InboxService)
    • util.JSONUtils
    • util.MailUtil
    • util.MyUtils
    • util.Static
    • model.User (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • action.UserAction (implements com.opensymphony.xwork2.ModelDriven<T>)
    • service.impl.UserServiceImpl (implements service.UserService)
